channel.title: TrisidiaX 317 V2! [Release!]
channel.description:
[center][size=18pt]Well guys! i am here back again for my V2 Release! If you Download Please give me some credit
[center] [size=16pt] Things i have changed! This list will tell you what i have Added or was Adding.[/size][/center]
[center][color=teal][size=15pt][Known Glitches][/size][/center] [center] [url=http://www.rswebclients.com/forum/Thread-How-to-fix-PK-POINT-reset-glitch-on-TrisidiaX-V2]Pk points reset when loging out[/url] -Trisidia/Me [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,560948.msg4093182.html#msg4093182]Black Phat fix In-Game[/url] -Credits: Turbo X Repz [/center]
[center][color=teal][size=15pt][In Progress][/size][/center]
[center] SOF [Squeal Of Fortune] This is now 50% just need spinning interface! Player Clipping Npc Clipping All Dupes either disabled or patched Adding in Price Checker - Interfaces freeze client.... Duel Arena Glitches [Not being able to attack while in duel, etc..]
[size=15pt][Things I Have Completed!][/size]
Added In Working MoneyPouch! Fixed the dupe in the MoneyPouch Fixed the Drop Dupe Added In Summoning Orb With Draining Fixed Cheat Egine Dupe! Added in custom items Added in [Server] Announcement when you get 99 [100% Working] Added in LevelPoints with a Store Added in custom GFX and Anime for some basic commands Added in Lottery, [Lottie] Disabled Shops for Users That Can Spawn Staff or players who can spawn can not attend in the lottery Added 2 Starters Per Ip Added Custom Log-ins when Staff Log in Fixed Total Level Donators need Donor points to use their Shops not cash[Makes it so reg players cant be teled there and buy the items] Vote4Cash Voting System with SOF Spins on claim 100% Timed mute 100% Timed Ban Fixed Smithing (x5, x10) Added 120 Dungeoneering Fixed The Arrow Dupe Glitch Added Server AutoSave Fixed Lag when banking all Added Player Titles Added Auto-Server Save Added UIDs Added in SOF InterFace Added in KillStreak Point System Made KS give you extra PK Points Re-Wrote Mage (Was totally loveed up on v1) Custom Npc Shops Added in dice command for Donator+ [size=16pt] AND SO MUCH MORE![/size]
[size=16pt] Now Enjoy these pics![/size][/center]
